      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZING MATILDA (1) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 36 from 62 starts. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest when second (17.44) at this track. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of five starts. Top prospect. PROTEGE (3) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (23.02) at Gawler in a Grade 6 over 400m. Bold showing expected. ROYALE MAPLE (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (20.47) at Angle Park behind Toledo in a Grade 6. The form out of his last race has been franked. Must be included in calculations. ELEGANT FLINT (5) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
